  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The European Cardiac CT Registry has the unique potential to provide important data that will
      help to clarify the clinical role of cardiac computed tomography (CT), to create guidelines
      and recommendations for its use, and to identify the most important areas that require
      specific further research.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
